content.rendered:
Directed by Mikael Marcimain.

Written by Karin Arrhenius. Kerstin Ekman. Pia Gradvall. Maren Louise Käehne. Nanna Westh.

Cast Liv Mjönes (Barbro Torbjörnsson). Pernilla August (Annie Raft (1991)). Alba August (Mia Raft (1991)). Asta Kamma August (Annie Raft (1973)). Alma Pöysti (Ylja Happoltati (1973)). Magnus Krepper (Petrus). Christian Fandango Sundgren (Dan Ulander (1973)). Magnus Roosmann (Åke Vemdahl). Cecilia Nilsson (Gudrun Brandberg (1991)). Sven Boräng (Biger Torbjörnsson (1973)). Emelie Garbers (Lotta). Erik Ehn (Johan Brandberg (1991). Nathalie Williamsdotter (Sabine Westdijk). Andreas Kundler (Dan Ulander (1991)). Jesper Sjölander (Björne Brandenberg (1991)). Tove Skeidsvoll (Elna Westlund). Pella Kagerman (Agenta). Liam Gabrielsson Lövbrand (Johan Brandberg (1973)). Anitta Suikkari (Ylja Happolati). Alva Adermark (Mia Raft (1973)). Ylva Lööf (Syster Märta). Magnus Schmitz (Kommissarie Barkfors). Lucas Grimstedt (Björne Brandberg (1973)). Ulf Rönnerstrand (Åke Vemdahl (1973)). Electra Hallman (Brita). Ingmar Virta (Lill-Ola Lennartsson). Rolf Degerlund (Torsten Brandberg). Harleen Kalkat (Önis).

Language Swedish.

Producers Piv Bernth. Anna Croneman. Lars Hermann. Kristian Hoberstorfer. Helene Lindholm. Sebastian Lückel. Thomas Nilsson. Christoph Pellander. Sandra Warg. Elisabeth Victoria Winther. Sandy Varo Jarrell.

Production Apple Tree Productions. Sveriges Television (SVT). Filmpool Nord.

No. of Seasons 1

No. of Episodes 6

Status On Going (2023–)
